 the subject into a state of suspended animation. For the creature, time ceases to flow and its condition becomes fixed. The creature does not grow older. Its body functions virtually cease, and no force or effect can harm it. This state persists until th
e magic is removed (such as by a successful }{\i\fs20\cf0 dispel magic }{\fs20\cf0 spell or a }{\i\fs20\cf0 freedom }{\fs20\cf0 spell).
