\par If you have at least 5 feet of web between you and an opponent, it provides cover. If you have at least 20 feet of web between you, it provides total cover.
\par The strands of a }{\i\fs20\cf0 web }{\fs20\cf0 spell are flammable. A magic }{\i\fs20\cf0 flaming sword }{\fs20\cf0 
