\par }{\i\fs20\cf0 Web }{\fs20\cf0 can be made permanent with a }{\i\fs20\cf0 permanency }{\fs20\cf0 spell. A permanent }{\i\fs20\cf0 web }{\fs20\cf0 that is damaged (but not destroyed) regrows in 10 minutes.
